<description>Enhanced the 'calculateStatus' function to provide precise delay metrics (e.g., '5m Late') and updated the Journey Timeline to replace 'EXPECTED' with these real-time status indicators. Retained requested visual feedback: departed/visited stations are orange, and currently occupied stations are pink with a solid dot icon.</description>
